Zora Neale Hurston’s WPA field recordings in Jacksonville, FL (1939)

Field Recordings T86-244

Zora Neale Hurston's WPA field recordings in Jacksonville, FL made for the Library of Congress on June 18, 1939 with Herbert Halpert. This recording is available on the Florida Memory Project.
